            <xs:documentation>
                Information om signering
                
                signatureTime: 
                    Tidpunkt fĂ¶r signering, format Ă…Ă…Ă…Ă…MMDDttmmss. 
                assignedEntity: 
                    Information om person som signerat dokumentet
            </xs:documentation>
        </xs:annotation>
        <xs:sequence>
